WEBVTT

00:00:00.750 --> 00:00:03.167
Begitu menyakitkan

00:00:03.708 --> 00:00:07.042
untuk menghadapi kondisi
planet kita saat ini.

00:00:08.333 --> 00:00:10.267
Mulai dari kebakaran hutan,

00:00:11.083 --> 00:00:12.933
sampah plastik di lautan,

00:00:13.292 --> 00:00:16.518
kehilangan spesies setiap harinya,

00:00:16.542 --> 00:00:18.042
migrasi.

00:00:19.417 --> 00:00:22.958
Mudah untuk merasa kewalahan.

00:00:24.208 --> 00:00:26.367
Mungkin sedikit merasa tak berguna.

00:00:27.167 --> 00:00:28.602
Tak berdaya.

00:00:29.458 --> 00:00:30.875
Marah.